You are helping build a personal portfolio site for a Senior Data Scientist.

Stack: Astro, Tailwind CSS, deployed on Vercel.
- No React unless explicitly requested
- No blog, no CMS
- Projects data lives in /content/projects.json
- Contact section is a mailto link only — no form, no API
- Keep components in /src/components as .astro files
- Mobile-first responsive design
- No unnecessary dependencies